Puppet module: sysctl

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages sysctl software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include sysctl              # Install and run sysctl with standard configurations.
include sysctl::disable     # Disable sysctl service.
include sysctl::disableboot # Disable sysctl service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include sysctl::absent      # Remove sysctl package.

DEPENDENCIES:
